item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

DAn0194:

He’s not asking if the variable needs to even be there he’s asking why the cmd is throwing that error.

If he is asking why the cmd is throwing the error, he’s obviously lacking in java knowledge. So why don’t you explain an error for once instead of telling em what to do without any actual help.

OP, you have 2 variables in the method levelUp that have the same name, and Java doesn’t exactly like that.

You’re probably going to have to remove one of the two ints, but you don’t want to remove the wrong one. As zyle said:
